<section class="faq-section" id="faq">
  <div class="faq-header">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <p>Everything you need to know about enrollment, school fees, and daily operations.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-container">
    <!-- Question 1 -->
    <details class="faq-item" open>
      <summary>What are the age requirements for new student enrollment?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>We welcome students across multiple grade thresholds. For Crèche/Nursery, children must be at least 1–3 years old. For Primary entry, children must be 5 years old by September of the academic year, and Secondary school entry starts at age 10–11.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <!-- Question 2 -->
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>How can I obtain a breakdown of the school fees structure?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
